title: Virtus eyes offshore expansion
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Virtus eyes offshore expansion Virtus eyes offshore expansion Next Story Prev Story 15 min ago Read more: The Age 
Virtus Health chief executive Sue Channon says the in vitro fertilisation provider will hunt for acquisitions in Britain as it fights off intensifying competition in its core Australian market. Ms Channon said Virtus, the world's first listed fertility services company when it floated on the ASX in June 2013 , intends to diversify its local business as well as grow offshore.
